          resistance [ <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">52</TIMEX>] as positively selected (<ENAMEX TYPE="CONTACT_INFO">N67, R70, W210,</ENAMEX>
          Y215, and <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">F215</ENAMEX>) or possibly positively selected (<NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">L41</NUMEX>) to
          HIV-1 (<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Fig</ENAMEX>. <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">4</NUMEX>). The exceptions, <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">two</NUMEX> mutations of codon
