          Sequences
          Nucleotide sequences were downloaded from <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">GenBank</ENAMEX> at
          the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">NIH</ENAMEX>. Sequences were included only if they were
          isolated in the field and were not obviously pseudogenes
